1. Install direnv

2. Put an .envrc and a requirements.txt in your directory.

3. Add the following contents to the .envrc file:
      
layout python3
pip install -r requirements.txt
[ -f .gitignore ] && cat .gitignore | grep "^\.direnv$" > /dev/null || echo -en "\n.direnv" >> .gitignore
[ -f .gitignore ] && cat .gitignore | grep "^\.direnv/$" > /dev/null || echo -en "\n#direnv stuff\n.direnv/" >> .gitignore
[ -f .gitignore ] && cat .gitignore | grep "^\.direnv/\*$" > /dev/null || echo -en "\n.direnv/*" >> .gitignore


